description: The Innovator Laddered Allocation Power Buffer ETF seeks to provide exposure to the investment results of the FTSE Laddered Power Buffer Strategy Index. The Index is comprised of an equal-weight allocation to each of the 12 Innovator U.S. Equity Power Buffer ETFs which provide the upside of U.S. equities, subject to caps, while buffering against the first 15% of U.S. equity losses.
name: Laddered Allocation Power Buffer ETF
